Borouge to Start $30 Million China Plant Mid-2012, Alrroya Says

-- B y   T a m a r a   W a l i d
-- 
2011-06-12T05:25:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/borouge-to-start-30-million-china-plant-mid-2012-alrroya-says.html
Borouge, the Abu Dhabi-based
plastics company, plans to start a $30 million compounding plant
in  China ’s Guangzhou province in the middle of next year,
 Alrroya reported , citing the company’s Deputy Chief Executive
Officer Lawrence Jones.  To contact the reporter on this story:
